==事故后续及调查==
[[莫桑比克|莫桑比克]]政府称将会进行全国哀悼。总统[[阿曼多·格布扎|阿曼多·格布扎]]对遇难者家属表示哀悼。莫桑比克航空表示将会提供法律咨询服务并设立了一个用来给乘客家属提供信息的热线。<ref name="afp">{{cite web|url=http://www.google.com/hostednews/afp/article/ALeqM5hp5Pj7x7ySo9xM7V8ISbe7Td-yEg?docId=b66178f8-7565-4131-8822-d406a86139b7&hl=en|title=Missing Mozambique plane wreck found in Namibia, 33 dead|publisher=AFP|date=2013-11-30|accessdate=2013-11-30|archive-date=2013-12-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131203120951/http://www.google.com/hostednews/afp/article/ALeqM5hp5Pj7x7ySo9xM7V8ISbe7Td-yEg?docId=b66178f8-7565-4131-8822-d406a86139b7&hl=en|dead-url=no}}</ref>

残骸的轨迹显示飞机触地之后在地面上继续滑行了几百码。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Drönare till hjälp vid katastrofer|url=https://www.vf.se/2013/12/22/dronare-till-hjalp-vid-katastrofer/|access-date=2021-08-21|date=2013-12-22|last=Fosselius-Peterson|first=Lena|work=Värmlands Folkblad|language=sv|archive-date=2021-08-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210821162918/https://www.vf.se/2013/12/22/dronare-till-hjalp-vid-katastrofer/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

两个黑匣子，[[駕駛艙通話記錄器|駕駛艙通話記錄器]]和[[飛行紀錄儀|飛行紀錄儀]]于四天内在事故现场被找到，接着被送到[[NTSB|NTSB]]以解读其中的数据。<ref name=AvHerald>{{cite web |url=http://avherald.com/h?article=46c3abde&opt=0 |title=Crash: LAM E190 over Botswana/Namibia on Nov 29th 2013, captain intentionally crashed aircraft |publisher=The Aviation Herald |date= |accessdate=2013-12-22 |archive-date=2020-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112010623/http://avherald.com/h?article=46c3abde&opt=0 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2013年12月21日，{{link-en|莫三比克民航機構|Mozambican Civil Aviation Institute}}（{{lang-pt|Instituto de Aviação Civil de Moçambique}}）发布了初步调查报告，报告指出，机长Herminio dos Santos Fernandes有明确意图想要将客机坠毁，并手动改变了自动驾驶的设定。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/africa/2013/12/pilot-deliberately-caused-namibia-crash-201312225824891819.html |title=Pilot 'deliberately' crashed Mozambique plane |publisher=''[[Al_Jazeera|Al Jazeera]]'' |date=2013-12-22 |accessdate=2013-12-22 |archive-date=2020-06-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200628214312/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/africa/2013/12/pilot-deliberately-caused-namibia-crash-201312225824891819.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>这份报告指出，飞机的原定高度被从38000英尺经过三次改变，最终下降到592英尺，随后更是设定为低于地面。航速也一样被手动改变了。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/africaandindianocean/mozambique/10533239/Mozambique-airline-captain-intentionally-crashed-plane.html |title=Mozambique airline captain 'intentionally' crashed plane |publisher=The Telegraph |date=2013-12-22 |accessdate=2013-12-22 |archive-date=2013-12-24 |archive-url=https://wayback.archive-it.org/all/20131224125901/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/africaandindianocean/mozambique/10533239/Mozambique-Airlines-captain-intentionally-crashed-plane.html |dead-url=no }}</ref> CVR捕捉到下降过程中驾驶舱中被触发的警报和副驾驶反复在驾驶舱外砸门的声音，表明他在坠毁前不久一直被锁在门外。<ref name=AvHerald/><ref name="YahooDec21">{{cite news|title=Mozambique airline captain 'intentionally' crashed: probe|publisher=Yahoo News|date=2013-12-21|url=http://news.yahoo.com/mozambique-airline-captain-39-intentionally-39-crashed-probe-222522028.html|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131224211520/http://news.yahoo.com/mozambique-airline-captain-39-intentionally-39-crashed-probe-222522028.html|archivedate=2013-12-24}}</ref>

